otationImage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"code":"UIImage","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}]}}}